      "HEADER": [
        "Home > Gamemastering > Bestiary > Dragons > Dragon Family > Black Dragon > Hatchling Black Dragon Table of Contents Scales the color of black armor this ferocious hatchling dragon while crowned with large curved pointy horns. Black Dragon, Hatchling (CR 2)",
