        "Space 2.5 ft.; Reach 0 ft. (2.5 ft. with bite)",
        "Special Attacks Breath Weapon (30-ft. line, 1d10 shadow damage, Reflex DC 11 half, usable every 1d4 rounds) Special Abilities Terror Touch"
      ],
